These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, reading, singing, sudoku, video-games
There 5 different types of food: pepper, spinach, onion, apricot, garlic
1. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
6. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
7. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the right of the person eating pepper##5
8. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |      3       |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby   | chess    | video-games   | reading      | sudoku  | singing    |
| Food   | pepper | garlic | onion | spinach | apricot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-2::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, animation, documentary, musical, spy
5 different games are played: snooker, domino, mah-jongg, billiard, bridge
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 2. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
 3. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 6. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 7. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
 8. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
 9. the person watching animation movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching animation movies is between the person playing billiard and the person playing bridge##2
11. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |      4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | action     | animation | documentary | spy    |
| Game     | domino | billiard | snooker   | bridge        | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-3::.
House: wooden, cottage, townhouse, farmhouse, ranch-style
The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, dancing, gardening, reading
1. the ranch-style house is in the middle##1
2. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is the wooden house##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
7. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
8. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the cottage house and the wooden house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |
| House   | townhouse   | cottage       | ranch-style         | wooden | farmhouse |
| Hobby      | dancing | card-games | board-games | gardening   | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-4::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, april, december, november, may
There are 5 different nationalities: british, canadian, indonesian, italian, russian
 1. the russian is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 2. the british is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is the italian##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the italian is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the british is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 7. the canadian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the canadian is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |    4     |     5      |
| Birthday   | november     | december  | may   | april      | august  |
| Nationality   | italian | russian | british | canadian | indonesian |

