.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-5::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, cabbage, papaya, pear, radish
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, dunhill, bluemaster, havana, alhambra
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is between the person eating radish and the dunhill-smoker##2
4. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
5. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person eating papaya##5
6. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |   5    |
| Food    | cabbage | artichoke | papaya     | pear     | radish |
| Cigar   | alhambra  | old-henry   | dunhill | bluemaster | havana |

