.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-6::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  analyst, project-manager, journalist, scientist, videographer
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, motorbike, taxi, van
 1. the project-manager is on the left or right of the scientist##3
 2. the videographer is in an odd position##4
 3. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 4. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
 5. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the person driving the van##5
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
 8. the scientist is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the journalist is on the left or right of the analyst##3
10. the person driving the van is on the left of the videographer##1
11. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the analyst##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Job   | journalist | analyst | videographer  | project-manager     | scientist  |
| Transport     | taxi    | van    | helicopter | motorbike | airplane |

