.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-7::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, juice, milk, soy-milk
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, cat, hedgehog, ferret, horse
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
5. the person drinking milk is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
7. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
8. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2   |   3   |     4     |   5   |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | milk  | fanta | soy-milk  | juice |
| Pet   | horse          | hedgehog | ferret | rabbit | cat   |

