.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-8::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, milk, tea, soy-milk, fanta
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, italian, nigerian
1. the person drinking water is the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the nigerian is on the right of the australian##1
6. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
7. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking water and the italian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |
| Beverage          | tea    | milk    | fanta | water | soy-milk   |
| Nationality   | canadian | italian | australian | nigerian  | argentine |

