2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
4. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
7. the person drinking water is the person who's birthday is in july##1
8. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |    4    |      5      |
| Beverage      | juice      | fanta      | water   | cola    | almond-milk |
| Birthday   | august | february | july | june | december   |

