 1. the videographer is on the left or right of the dancercher##3
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 4. the journalist is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the journalist is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 7. the dancercher is somewhere to the right of the musician##5
 8. the journalist is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 9. the journalist is between the musician and the dancercher##2
10. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |    5     |
| Job   | dancer     | musician       | journalist    | dancercher | videographer |
| Hobby      | writing | card-games | dancing | camping | fishing  |

