2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is in an odd position##4
4. the malaysian is the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
6. the malaysian is between the japanese and the spanish##2
7. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
9. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |     4     |    5    |
| City          | hamburg  | berlin  | marseilles    | nizza | liverpool  |
| Nationality   | nigerian | russian | japanese | malaysian | spanish |

