.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-14::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, librarian, teacher, videographer, writer
There are 5 different favourite colors: pink, amber, chestnut, orange, black
1. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
2. the accountant is between the teacher and the person who likes chestnut##2
3. the writer is somewhere to the right of the person who likes orange##5
4. the accountant is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
5. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
6. the person who likes orange is in an even position##4
7. the librarian is the person who likes orange##1
8. the person who likes pink is the accountant##1
9. the person who likes amber is between the person who likes orange and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |    5    |
| Job   | videographer | accountant | teacher    | librarian | writer  |
| Color   | chestnut       | pink       | amber | orange  | black |

