.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-16::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, magic-tricks, singing, skydiving, traveling
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball, tennis, golf, parkour
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
9. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3       |     4     |    5    |
| Hobby         | hiking  | traveling | magic-tricks | skydiving | singing |
| Sport   | golf | tennis   | volleyball   | surfing | parkour |

