.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, milk, mirinda, sprite
5 different games are played: go, bridge, billiard, canasta, mah-jongg
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
2. the person playing go is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
6. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
7. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |
| Beverage      | milk      | iced-tea | mirinda | sprite    | lemonade  |
| Game   | billiard | bridge   | mah-jongg | go | canasta |

