4. the photographer is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
5. the mechanic is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
6. the mechanic is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |      2       |     3      |      4       |    5     |
| Transport   | ship      | taxi     | car      | trike       | quad-bike    |
| Job        | librarian | entrepreneur | journalist | photographer | mechanic |

 